<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> بابٌ: كَيْفَ كَانَتْ يَمِينُ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ سَعْدٌ:</span> قالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«وَالَّذِي نَفْسِي بِيَدِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ أَبُو قَتَادَةَ:</span> قالَ أَبُو بَكْرٍ عِنْدَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: لَاهَا اللَّهِ إِذًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> وَاللَّهِ وَبِاللَّهِ وَتَاللَّهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>